Subject: Java Email Fix

The message builder in your Java example wasn’t properly set up — here's the fixed snippet: import javax.mail.*;
import javax.mail.internet.*;

public class EmailSender {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws Exception {
        MimeMessage msg = new MimeMessage(Session.getDefaultInstance(System.getProperties()));
        msg.setFrom("me@example.com");
        msg.addRecipient(Message.RecipientType.TO, new InternetAddress("contact@contact.com"));
        msg.setText("confirmation");
        Transport.send(msg);
    }
}

